      <t>&lt;p&gt;This document specifies a set of extensions to the Teredo protocol.  These extensions provide additional capabilities to Teredo, including support for more types of Network Address Translations (NATs) and support for more efficient communication. [STANDARDS-TRACK]&lt;/p&gt;</t>
